## Final report

Your final message is the ONLY thing that reaches the parent session — everything else (command output, diffs, intermediate reasoning) stays isolated here and is never seen. Return **exactly one line**: what changed + the PR URL. No preamble, no step recap, no markdown headers. If you stopped early (main/master, or nothing staged), your one line explains why and nothing else.
